While congratulations are still in order for superstar Rihanna, Nigerian songstress Seyi Shay has taken to her social media page to disclose that she has been aware of the pregnancy since last year.
The controversial Seyi Shay felicitated with the Barbadian singer and entrepreneur like many other celebrities on micro-blogging and social media platform, Twitter.
In Seyi Shay’s post, the ‘Right Now’ crooner wrote; Big Congratulations to @rihanna. This is the best news I’ve heard this year (but knew since last year).”
ALSO READ: “Rihanna is pregnant and I’m still single”
Big Congratulations to @rihanna  This is the best news I’ve heard this year (but knew since last year) … 
— Seyi Shay BIGGIRL LIVE IN LONDON 25/26 FEB (@iamseyishay) February 1, 2022
National Daily had reported on Monday, January 31, 2022, that Rihanna and her rapper sweetheart, A$AP Rocky, are expecting their first child together.
The ‘Umbrella’ singer debuted her baby bump in a pink jacket, which bared her bump, while she donned a blue baggy jeans to complete her fashion style.






